        -:  103:/**
        -:  104: * We do not allow List(RTYPE=VECSXP), RawVector(RTYPE=RAWSXP)
        -:  105: * or ExpressionVector(RTYPE=EXPRSXP) to be sorted, so it is
        -:  106: * desirable to issue a compiler error if user attempts to sort
