        -:  108: *
        -:  109: * We declare a template class without defining the generic
        -:  110: * class body, but complete the definition in specialization
        -:  111: * of qualified Vector types. Hence when using this class
        -:  112: * on unqualified Vectors, the compiler will emit errors.
        -:  113: */
        -:  114:template<int RTYPE>
        -:  115:class Sort_is_not_allowed_for_this_type;
